fulltitle: James Jesus Angleton and the JFK Assassination w/ Author Lisa Pease
title: James Jesus Angleton and the JFK Assassination w/ Author Lisa Pease
_filename: _James Jesus Angleton and the JFK Assassination w_ Author Lisa Pease.webm
description:
Lisa Pease, long time researcher of the cold war assassinations and author of a forthcoming book on the RFK assassination entitled "A Lie Too Big To Fail" (Sept. 2018) talks about James Jesus Angleton and the murder of President John F. Kennedy.

For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
